'''Swilja''' was a legendary princess in the [[Twi'lek/Legends|Twi'lek]] culture, thought to be beautiful.

Many female Twi'leks were named after her, like [[Jedi Knight/Legends|Jedi Knight]] [[Swilja Fenn]].

